      • newColumnInstance

        public CellColumn newColumnInstance(int initialCapacity)
        Returns the column instance to be used by the ColumnWorker. By default, this is the regular CellColumn. Override this in subclasses if u need a different Column instance.
        Parameters:
        initialCapacity - TODO
        Returns:
        the new instantiated column instance. The column name is taken from the ColumnWorker's columnName property.
